      ##Compatibility

      Gem is compatible with [**Ruby**](https://www.ruby-lang.org/ "Ruby") version 2.x.x and [**Ruby On Rails**](http://rubyonrails.org/ "Rails") 4.2.x and 5.x.x.

  %div
    :markdown

      ##Simple form

      Gem is compatible with  [simple_form](https://github.com/plataformatec/simple_form).
      All inputs fields can be used with **simple_form**.
